TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT DISTINCT TR.TEST_ROSTER_ID, TR.CUSTOMER_ID, TR.STUDENT_ID, TR.OPUNIT, TR.TEST_ADMIN_ID
FROM STUDENT ST, TEST_ROSTER TR, TEST_ADMIN TA, TEST_CATALOG TC, ORG_NODE_STUDENT ONS, ORG_NODE ONODE, ORG_NODE_PARENT ONP, ORG_NODE_PARENT ONP2, ORG_NODE ONODE2, EISS_ORG_BC_TPE TPE, ORG_NODE_CATEGORY ONC, STG_EXPORT_PARMS PARAMS WHERE ST.STUDENT_ID = TR.STUDENT_ID AND TR.TEST_ADMIN_ID = TA.TEST_ADMIN_ID AND TA.TEST_CATALOG_ID = TC.TEST_CATALOG_ID AND TR.CUSTOMER_ID =$$CUSTOMER_ID AND TR.CUSTOMER_ID = TA.CUSTOMER_ID AND PARAMS.CUSTOMER_ID = TR.CUSTOMER_ID AND TA.PRODUCT_ID = TC.PRODUCT_ID AND TA.PRODUCT_ID = $$PRODUCT_ID AND TPE.CUSTOMER_ID = $$CUSTOMER_ID AND TPE.PRODUCT_ID = $$PRODUCT_ID AND TR.ACTIVATION_STATUS = 'AC' AND TR.STUDENT_ID = ONS.STUDENT_ID -- AND TR.ORG_NODE_ID = ONS.ORG_NODE_ID AND ONP.ORG_NODE_ID = TR.ORG_NODE_ID AND ONP.PARENT_ORG_NODE_ID = ONODE.ORG_NODE_ID AND ONC.ORG_NODE_CATEGORY_ID = ONODE.ORG_NODE_CATEGORY_ID AND ONC.CATEGORY_NAME = 'School' AND ONODE.ORG_NODE_ID = ONP2.ORG_NODE_ID AND ONP2.PARENT_ORG_NODE_ID = ONODE2.ORG_NODE_ID AND ONODE.ORG_NODE_CODE = TPE.ORG_NODE_CODE AND ONODE2.ORG_NODE_CODE = TPE.PARENT_SPCL_CODE AND TR.TEST_COMPLETION_STATUS NOT IN ('NT', 'SC') AND NVL(TR.DNS_STATUS,'N') !='Y' AND PARAMS.PARAMETER = 'CALIBRATION' AND TPE.CALIBRATION = PARAMS.VALUE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT
se.customer_id, se.product_id, se.ou_id, se.opunit, MAX(c.eiss_org || LPAD(p.eiss_testing_program, 3, 0)) org_test_prog, MAX(e.struc_lvl) struc_lvl, MAX(e.struc_elm) struc_elm, MAX(e.next_op_unit_num) next_op_unit_num, MAX(e.elm_name) org_node_name, e.calibration as calibration, e.public_org as public_org, p.eiss_testing_program as testing_prog
FROM STG_EISS_TB se, org_node n, product p, customer c, EISS_ORG_BC_TPE e
WHERE
level_type = 'SH' AND n.org_node_id = se.ou_id AND p.product_id = se.product_id AND c.customer_id = se.customer_id AND n.org_node_code = e.org_node_code(+) AND e.parent_spcl_code = e.org_node_code AND c.customer_id = e.customer_id AND p.product_id = e.product_id
GROUP BY se.customer_id, se.product_id, se.ou_id, se.opunit, e.calibration, e.public_org, p.eiss_testing_program

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT DISTINCT stg.customer_id AS customer_id, stg.product_id AS product_id,
tr.org_node_id AS gh_id,
tr.student_id AS student_id, str.opunit AS OPUNIT, '"' || SUBSTR(UPPER (st.last_name),1,30) || '"' AS last_name, '"' || SUBSTR(UPPER (st.first_name),1,30) || '"' AS first_name, '"' || SUBSTR(UPPER (st.middle_name),1,1) || '"' AS middle_name, st.birthdate AS birthdate, DECODE (st.gender, 'M', 'M', 'F', 'F', NULL ) AS gender, st.grade AS grade
FROM student st, test_roster tr, STG_PARAM_WINSCR_TB stg, STG_TEST_ROSTER str
WHERE
st.student_id = tr.student_id AND str.student_id = st.student_id AND tr.customer_id = stg.customer_id AND str.test_roster_id = tr.test_roster_id AND str.student_id = tr.student_id
